    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you make it a bit more descriptive of the people themselves? Like, describe their appearance and their way of life in a way that emphasizes how much they lack the structure and sophistication of European society. Make it sound like he's looking down on them as being almost childlike or unevolved.",
